# The Amazing Digital Cloud! ☁️
# IMAGE: $/previews/tadc.png
# DESC: An Introduction to Hosting.

I had the honor of being invited back to my oldstomping grounds to host a workshop at [HackKU26|https://hackku.org]. This workshop
was more hands on than my usual talks, with a large portion of the content revolving around bringing up a servers 
together on [Digital Ocean|https://www.digitalocean.com/], who was a sponsor of the event.

